---
layout: base.njk
title: Продукти
description: Всички продукти в мрежа
pagination:
    data: products
    size: 1000
    alias: allProducts
---

<section class="py-12 bg-primary-sand/30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="w-full text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-evergreen">Продукти</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-primary-deepsea max-w-3xl">Разгледайте всички продукти BIO VEL.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            {% for product in allProducts %}
            <a href="/produkti/{{ product.meta_title }}/" class="group rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-md overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <div class="w-full h-48 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center bg-white">
                    <img src="{{ product.images[0] }}" alt="{{ product.title }}" class="max-h-40 object-contain group-hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-300">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-deepsea">{{ product.title }}</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary-dark-gray">{{ product.short_description }}</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


